text: Aleksandra Kovačević was crowned Miss Earth Bosnia & Herzegovina 2011. She competed at Miss Earth finals held on 3 December 2011 at the University of the Philippines Theater in Diliman, Quezon City, Philippines and placed in Top 8."Aleksandra Kovačević Crowned Miss Earth Bosnia & Herzegovina 2011" ==References== Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina female models Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Serbian female models Category:Miss Earth 2011 contestants Category:Serbs of Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Serb models
